HIV Prevalence in Balaka

For a detailed methodology on how these maps were created, please refer to the supplementary material.

District Map

The following interactive map shows HIV prevalence estimates across Balaka at the district, traditional authority, and 1x1km pixel levels. Health facility locations and details are also shown.
